# NEXUS Frontend
# Nusxalang: .env nomiga. Vercel da Settings → Environment Variables.

# Faqat GitHub + Supabase + Vercel deploy uchun (boshqa server kerak emas):
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://xxxxx.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJhbGciOi...

# Lokalda Node API (nexus-api) ishlatish uchun — Supabase o'rniga:
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:3001
# (Agar VITE_SUPABASE_URL ham bo'lsa, Supabase ustun qoladi)
